Make lib:
  Playlist:
    - Support stepping back to previous position in playlist.
    - Support getting track from playlist by index.
    - Support saving named playlist state to disk (~/.korama/playlists/<name>)
    - Support loading saved playlists.
    - Support listing saved playlists.
    - Support <DYNAMIC> tag in playlist- adds a new track at random from a specific music library or playlist. (trait)
